one_reviews_text:
I only have sound from the metronome.

review_feedback: This bug has been fixed in recent updates. We're sorry you had a bad first experience, but thanks for letting us know about the issue. We hope to have you back soon!
Can you try restarting Oculus and the game, and checking your volume settings? If it's still not working, please email me at support@jamhack.games and we'll get it figured out!
